    "causal_summary": "The deep review found 295 broken markdown links across skills/commands/agents because feature removal/migration/deprecation edits deleted snippet files or moved targets without updating the hand-maintained `feature_catalog.md` / `manual_testing_playbook.md` roots and other cross-references — and nothing failed, so the debt accumulated silently. Existing checks do not cover this: `scripts/check-links.sh` validates only wikilinks (`[[...]]`), is opt-in, and is not CI-wired; `rules/check-phase-links.sh` only checks phase folders.",
